COMMERCIAL USE
--------------
If you want to build a product around the TBD platform, two options are
designed for you:

  - TBD-Core: Our core DSP board with all audio, MIDI, and USB I/O
    assembled. Connect your own UI board via the 30-pin FFC connector
    and design your own enclosure.
  - Custom Integration: We integrate the ESP32-P4, RP2350, and codec
    directly onto your PCB for full control over form factor, connectors,
    and BOM.

We also offer volume pricing for TBD-16 units used as finished components
inside your products.

See https://dadamachines.com/contact/ for details.

If you modify the dadamachines-added code (WebUI, tools, documentation) and
distribute it, those modifications must be released under LGPL 3.0. If you
would like to keep your modifications proprietary, dadamachines can provide
a commercial license. Contact us: https://dadamachines.com/contact/


